OL,3,CBaldoni and wife say Lively lawsuit
OL,4,Cwas 'injustice disguised as fight for
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FVideo credit: Instagram /
OL,8,F@justinbaldoni
OL,10,FJustin Baldoni and his wife Emily have
OL,11,Fspoken out about their legal battle
OL,12,Fwith Blake Lively for the first time,
OL,13,Fdescribing it as an "injustice" that
OL,14,Fwas "disguised as a fight for women".
OL,16,FBaldoni, 42, and Lively, 38, ended
OL,17,Ftheir dispute over the movie It Ends
OL,18,FWith Us with a settlement in May,
OL,19,Fbefore it was due to go to trial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
