OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783631508
OL,3,CBaldoni and wife say Lively lawsuit
OL,4,Cwas 'injustice disguised as fight for
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,F"We have not spoken publicly for the
OL,8,Fbetter part of the last two years, and
OL,9,Fit's not because we haven't had
OL,10,Fanything to say, because Lord knows we
OL,11,Fhave," Baldoni began in a video he
OL,12,Ffilmed with his wife Emily and posted
OL,13,Fon Instagram.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783631508
OL,3,CBaldoni and wife say Lively lawsuit
OL,4,Cwas 'injustice disguised as fight for
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,F"There is so much to say and it makes
OL,8,Fit hard to speak (...) but what does
OL,9,Ffeel important is that we can
OL,10,Fgenuinely say that we are sitting here
OL,11,Ftoday feeling immense gratitude for so
OL,12,Fmany things, and so many people, and
OL,13,Fso many things that have happened to
OL,14,Fus," Emily continued.
OL,16,F"But I also feel that it's important
OL,17,Fas we say that - it doesn't negate the
OL,18,Finjustice and the pain that we have
OL,19,Falso felt in the last few years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
