OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783631508
OL,3,CBaldoni and wife say Lively lawsuit
OL,4,Cwas 'injustice disguised as fight for
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,F"We've had to wrestle with so many
OL,8,Fthings and try to understand so many
OL,9,Fthings, like how could something like
OL,10,Fthis even happen, let alone disguised
OL,11,Fas a fight for women. So much to
OL,12,Funpack.
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
