OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783631508
OL,3,CBaldoni and wife say Lively lawsuit
OL,4,Cwas 'injustice disguised as fight for
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,F"And the truth is, the reality is that
OL,8,Fthere's been a lot of trauma for us to
OL,9,Fmove through as a family, which also
OL,10,Fmakes it hard to speak."
OL,12,FLively sued Baldoni and Wayfarer
OL,13,FStudios in December 2024, alleging on-
OL,14,Fset sexual harassment, a hostile work
OL,15,Fenvironment and a calculated "smear
OL,16,Fcampaign" against her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
