OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783631508
OL,3,CBaldoni and wife say Lively lawsuit
OL,4,Cwas 'injustice disguised as fight for
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FBaldoni, the director of It Ends With
OL,8,FUs, denied the claims and launched a
OL,9,Fcountersuit against Lively and her
OL,10,Fhusband, Ryan Reynolds, accusing them
OL,11,Fof defamation and extortion. This was
OL,12,Fdismissed in 2025.
OL,14,FIn April 2026, a judge dismissed 10
OL,15,Fout of 13 of Lively's claims, before a
OL,16,Fsettlement took place between both
OL,17,Fparties shortly before the trial was
OL,18,Fdue to begin in May.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783631508
OL,3,CBaldoni and wife say Lively lawsuit
OL,4,Cwas 'injustice disguised as fight for
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FNeither Lively nor Baldoni received
OL,8,Fany money in the settlement, but
OL,9,FLively is able to reclaim legal costs
OL,10,Fof $8 million (about #5.96 million),
OL,11,Fout of her demanded $300 million (#224
OL,12,Fmillion) in fees and damages, through
OL,13,Fa law designed to protect survivors of
OL,14,Fsexual harassment.
OL,16,F"There have been so many painful
OL,17,Fthings that have been spoken into
OL,18,Fexistence over the last couple of
OL,19,Fyears, and that created so much
OL,20,Fnoise," Baldoni said in the video.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783631508
OL,3,CBaldoni and wife say Lively lawsuit
OL,4,Cwas 'injustice disguised as fight for
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,F"We didn't want to add to the noise.
OL,8,FSo we just wanted to let the justice
OL,9,Fsystem run its course."
OL,11,FBoth sides classed the ruling over
OL,12,FLively's legal costs as a victory for
OL,13,Fthemselves.
OL,15,FLively's lawyers said the award of
OL,16,Flegal fees made it clear the actress
OL,17,Fhad "brought her claims in good faith,
OL,18,Fthat there was no evidence she acted
OL,19,Fwith malice, and that she is the
OL,20,Fprevailing defendant".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783631508
OL,3,CBaldoni and wife say Lively lawsuit
OL,4,Cwas 'injustice disguised as fight for
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,FBut Baldoni's lawyer said Lively had
OL,8,F"pivoted to exploit a California law"
OL,9,Fto receive damages after she failed to
OL,10,Fget her demands for $300 million.
OL,12,FThe law is intended to protect victims
OL,13,Fof sexual harassment or assault from
OL,14,Fretaliatory lawsuits meant to
OL,15,Fintimidate and silence them.
OL,17,F"Throughout this process, innocent
OL,18,Fpeople had their reputations unfairly
OL,19,Ftarnished. There was no sexual
OL,20,Fharassment. There was no retaliation,"
OL,21,FBaldoni's lawyer said.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@eO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
