OL,3,CBaldoni and wife say Lively lawsuit
OL,4,Cwas 'injustice disguised as fight for
OL,5,Cwomen'
OL,7,F"There was no smear campaign. The
OL,8,Fcourt recognised it, the record
OL,9,Freflects it, and we have maintained it
OL,10,Ffrom the very beginning."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
